to the money and livestock...

104
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,672
...the groom paid the bride's father.

105
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:23,150
For example, you're adorable,
intelligent and a good earner.

106
00:05:23,319 --> 00:05:26,948
